              <button class="faq-toggle">
                <h3 class="faq-title">
                  <span class="faq-title-span">What Is The Return Policy?</span>
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
                    <path d="m48.707 13.853-1.414-1.413L25 34.732 2.707 12.44l-1.414 1.413L25 37.56z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </h3>
                <p class="faq-text">
                  All pieces are brand new out of the package — no returns or exchanges and all sales are final.
                </p>
              </button>
            </div>

            <div class="faq">
              <button class="faq-toggle">
                <h3 class="faq-title">
                  <span class="faq-title-span">What Is The EU / UK Return Policy?</span>
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
                    <path d="m48.707 13.853-1.414-1.413L25 34.732 2.707 12.44l-1.414 1.413L25 37.56z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </h3>
                <p class="faq-text">
                  All pieces are brand new out of the package — no returns or exchanges and all sales are final.
                </p>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="accordion-item" data-accordion-item="" data-block-id="">
        <a
          href="#"
          class="accordion-title"
          aria-controls="lowns1-accordion"
          id="lowns1-accordion-label"
          aria-expanded="false"
        >
          FAQ
        </a>
        <div
          class="rte accordion-content"
          data-tab-content=""
          role="region"
          aria-labelledby="lowns1-accordion-label"
          aria-hidden="true"
          id="lowns1-accordion"
        >
          <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq">
              <button class="faq-toggle">
                <h3 class="faq-title">
                  <span class="faq-title-span"> Where Is Yellow Label Co. Made? </span>
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
                    <path d="m48.707 13.853-1.414-1.413L25 34.732 2.707 12.44l-1.414 1.413L25 37.56z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </h3>
                <p class="faq-text">
                  Yellow Label Co. is designed in New York City and handcrafted from scratch in Los Angeles.
                </p>
              </button>
            </div>

            <div class="faq">
              <button class="faq-toggle">
                <h3 class="faq-title">
                  <span class="faq-title-span"> How Can I Find Out About Upcoming Style Releases? </span>
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
                    <path d="m48.707 13.853-1.414-1.413L25 34.732 2.707 12.44l-1.414 1.413L25 37.56z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </h3>
                <p class="faq-text">
                  Stay up to date with our new releases and drops via subscribing to our emails and following us on
                  instagram at @yellowlabelco.
                </p>
              </button>
            </div>

            <div class="faq">
              <button class="faq-toggle">
                <h3 class="faq-title">
                  <span class="faq-title-span"> How Do I Know My Size? </span>
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
                    <path d="m48.707 13.853-1.414-1.413L25 34.732 2.707 12.44l-1.414 1.413L25 37.56z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </h3>
                <p class="faq-text">
                  To best gauge your appropriate size, please refer to the sizing chart for the particular item you’re
                  interested in. Any other questions please e-mail
                  <a href="mailto:hello@yellowlabel.co">hello@yellowlabel.co</a>hello@yellowlabel.co
                </p>
              </button>
            </div>

            <div class="faq">
              <button class="faq-toggle">
                <h3 class="faq-title">
                  <span class="faq-title-span"> DO THE GARMENTS BLEED? </span>
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
                    <path d="m48.707 13.853-1.414-1.413L25 34.732 2.707 12.44l-1.414 1.413L25 37.56z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </h3>
                <p class="faq-text">Wash the garments alone for the first wash due to color bleeding.</p>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
   $(document).ready(function() {
     $(".accordion-title").click(function() {
       $(this).next().toggleClass("active");
       $(this).toggleClass("is-active");
     });

  $(".faq-toggle").click(function() {
     $(this).find(".faq-text").toggleClass("active");
   });
   });
</script>

